505
00:28:41,019 --> 00:28:42,960
[SPEAKER_00] od ljubavi koja dodine moje srce,

506
00:28:42,960 --> 00:28:44,259
[SPEAKER_00] od radice koja ispuni ponekad,

507
00:28:44,259 --> 00:28:45,480
[SPEAKER_00] nenadno moje srce,

508
00:28:45,480 --> 00:28:46,380
[SPEAKER_00] sve je to dar.

509
00:28:46,380 --> 00:28:47,839
[SPEAKER_00] Sve.

510
00:28:47,839 --> 00:28:49,900
[SPEAKER_00] I kako onda ne zahvaljivati?

511
00:28:49,900 --> 00:28:51,240
[SPEAKER_00] Ali zanimljivo,

512
00:28:51,240 --> 00:28:52,140
[SPEAKER_00] kad zahvaljujemo,

513
00:28:52,140 --> 00:28:53,319
[SPEAKER_00] što se događa?

514
00:28:53,319 --> 00:28:54,700
[SPEAKER_00] Srce nam se otvara

515
00:28:54,700 --> 00:28:56,079
[SPEAKER_00] za ono što je Bog već prepremio.

516
00:28:56,079 --> 00:28:57,440
[SPEAKER_00] Bog već daje nove darove.

517
00:28:57,440 --> 00:28:58,660
[SPEAKER_00] Već su tu.

518
00:28:58,660 --> 00:29:00,220
[SPEAKER_00] I kako će Bože hvalati?

519
00:29:00,220 --> 00:29:02,140
[SPEAKER_00] On već novi dar daje u srce,

520
00:29:02,140 --> 00:29:02,880
[SPEAKER_00] novi blagoslov.

521
00:29:03,940 --> 00:29:05,119
[SPEAKER_00] Zato je silno važno

522
00:29:05,119 --> 00:29:06,619
[SPEAKER_00] znati i zahvaljivati.

523
00:29:06,619 --> 00:29:08,220
[SPEAKER_01] Onda isto tako možemo reći

524
00:29:08,220 --> 00:29:09,859
[SPEAKER_01] da je svaka molitva jednako vrijedna?

525
00:29:09,859 --> 00:29:12,579
[SPEAKER_00] Pa postoje različite vrste molitava.

526
00:29:12,579 --> 00:29:14,920
[SPEAKER_00] Ako je riječ o vrstama molitve,

527
00:29:14,920 --> 00:29:16,779
[SPEAKER_00] postoje molitva zahvaljivanja,

528
00:29:16,779 --> 00:29:17,599
[SPEAKER_00] molitva klanjanja,

529
00:29:17,599 --> 00:29:18,440
[SPEAKER_00] molitva klicanja,

530
00:29:18,440 --> 00:29:20,059
[SPEAKER_00] molitva prošnje.

531
00:29:21,420 --> 00:29:21,839
[SPEAKER_00] Dakle,

532
00:29:21,839 --> 00:29:25,200
[SPEAKER_00] Isus kaže,

533
00:29:25,200 --> 00:29:28,019
[SPEAKER_00] što god zaištete od Moog Otca,

534
00:29:28,019 --> 00:29:28,480
[SPEAKER_00] da će vam.

535
00:29:28,480 --> 00:29:31,720
[SPEAKER_00] Tražite, naći ćete.

536
00:29:31,720 --> 00:29:33,619
[SPEAKER_00] Kucajte, otvorit će vam se.

537
00:29:33,619 --> 00:29:35,180
[SPEAKER_00] Pitajte, da će vam se.

538
00:29:35,180 --> 00:29:36,339
[SPEAKER_00] Dakle,

539
00:29:36,339 --> 00:29:38,880
[SPEAKER_00] Otac je pun ljubavi,

540
00:29:38,880 --> 00:29:41,160
[SPEAKER_00] ali često puta,

541
00:29:41,160 --> 00:29:42,500
[SPEAKER_00] zašto imamo dojam

542
00:29:42,500 --> 00:29:43,759
[SPEAKER_00] da molitve nismo slišani?

543
00:29:44,259 --> 00:29:45,960
[SPEAKER_00] Jer molimo što nije za naše dobro.

544
00:29:45,960 --> 00:29:48,160
[SPEAKER_00] Daću jedan primjer,

545
00:29:48,160 --> 00:29:49,740
[SPEAKER_00] možda bezvezan.

546
00:29:49,740 --> 00:29:51,099
[SPEAKER_00] Neko moli,

547
00:29:51,099 --> 00:29:52,259
[SPEAKER_00] daj me da dobijem na lutri

548
00:29:52,259 --> 00:29:54,119
[SPEAKER_00] milijon eura.

549
00:29:54,119 --> 00:29:56,240
[SPEAKER_00] Ok,

550
00:29:56,240 --> 00:29:57,460
[SPEAKER_00] Bog to može učiniti.

551
00:29:57,460 --> 00:30:00,599
[SPEAKER_00] Ali Bog zna ishod toga

552
00:30:00,599 --> 00:30:03,079
[SPEAKER_00] da će vam možda milijon eura

553
00:30:03,079 --> 00:30:03,900
[SPEAKER_00] upropasiti život.

554
00:30:03,900 --> 00:30:05,279
[SPEAKER_00] I naravno,

555
00:30:05,279 --> 00:30:06,180
[SPEAKER_00] kao dobar roditelj,

556
00:30:06,180 --> 00:30:07,220
[SPEAKER_00] neće ga uslišati.

557
00:30:07,220 --> 00:30:10,640
[SPEAKER_00] Ali ako mi molimo,

558
00:30:10,640 --> 00:30:11,619
[SPEAKER_00] daj mi svoga duha,

559
00:30:11,619 --> 00:30:13,140
[SPEAKER_00] daj mi svoj blagoslov,

560
00:30:14,220 --> 00:30:15,519
[SPEAKER_00] Bog će to rado napraviti,

561
00:30:15,519 --> 00:30:16,440
[SPEAKER_00] jer to znaše dobro.

562
00:30:16,440 --> 00:30:19,259
[SPEAKER_00] Daj mi dar opraštanja,

563
00:30:19,259 --> 00:30:20,700
[SPEAKER_00] daj mi dar ljubavi,

564
00:30:20,700 --> 00:30:21,960
[SPEAKER_00] dar mi dar dobrote,

565
00:30:21,960 --> 00:30:23,839
[SPEAKER_00] daj mi mudrost.

566
00:30:23,839 --> 00:30:25,519
[SPEAKER_00] Jako kaže u svojoj poslanci,

567
00:30:25,519 --> 00:30:26,420
[SPEAKER_00] svaki dobar dar

568
00:30:26,420 --> 00:30:27,519
[SPEAKER_00] dolazi od ozgor.

569
00:30:27,519 --> 00:30:28,880
[SPEAKER_00] Ako dolazi od ozgora,

570
00:30:28,880 --> 00:30:29,680
[SPEAKER_00] moram nam moliti.

571
00:30:29,680 --> 00:30:33,019
[SPEAKER_00] Moram imati otvorno srce

572
00:30:33,019 --> 00:30:34,319
[SPEAKER_00] za primiti ono što Bog nudi.

573
00:30:34,319 --> 00:30:36,420
[SPEAKER_00] A nudi toliko toga.

574
00:30:36,420 --> 00:30:38,779
[SPEAKER_01] Što biste savjetovali nekome

575
00:30:38,779 --> 00:30:40,200
[SPEAKER_01] ako u istinu želi naučiti

576
00:30:40,200 --> 00:30:41,059
[SPEAKER_01] pravilno moliti?

577
00:30:41,059 --> 00:30:42,700
[SPEAKER_01] Kako danas moliti?

578
00:30:42,700 --> 00:30:43,920
[SPEAKER_00] Pa ja bih ću nam reći

579
00:30:43,920 --> 00:30:45,859
[SPEAKER_00] studentima da postoje

580
00:30:45,859 --> 00:30:49,220
[SPEAKER_00] četir razine molitve.

581
00:30:49,220 --> 00:30:51,180
[SPEAKER_00] Na prvoj razini

582
00:30:51,180 --> 00:30:52,500
[SPEAKER_00] ja govorim,

583
00:30:52,500 --> 00:30:53,700
[SPEAKER_00] ne čujem nija ni Bog.

584
00:30:53,700 --> 00:30:55,299
[SPEAKER_00] To je naša

585
00:30:55,299 --> 00:30:56,359
[SPEAKER_00] najredovitija molitva,

586
00:30:56,359 --> 00:30:57,559
[SPEAKER_00] naša najčešća molitva.

587
00:30:57,559 --> 00:30:58,559
[SPEAKER_00] Dakle, molimo molitvo

588
00:30:58,559 --> 00:30:59,079
[SPEAKER_00] očinaša,

589
00:30:59,079 --> 00:30:59,740
[SPEAKER_00] zdravo Marije,

590
00:30:59,740 --> 00:31:00,759
[SPEAKER_00] molitvo krunice,

591
00:31:00,759 --> 00:31:01,619
[SPEAKER_00] ali mi svećanici

592
00:31:01,619 --> 00:31:03,619
[SPEAKER_00] božanski časaslov,

593
00:31:03,619 --> 00:31:05,180
[SPEAKER_00] ali smo praktički

594
00:31:05,180 --> 00:31:06,759
[SPEAKER_00] sve sveli samo na riječi.

595
00:31:07,920 --> 00:31:08,579
[SPEAKER_00] A Isus kaže,

596
00:31:08,579 --> 00:31:10,599
[SPEAKER_00] ovaj mi naroštuje usnama,

597
00:31:10,599 --> 00:31:11,839
[SPEAKER_00] srce moje daleko od mene.

598
00:31:11,839 --> 00:31:13,799
[SPEAKER_00] I ne mislite da ćete zbog mnoštva riječi

599
00:31:13,799 --> 00:31:14,640
[SPEAKER_00] biti uslišani.

600
00:31:15,140 --> 00:31:18,019
[SPEAKER_00] Gospodin Isus prekorava

601
00:31:18,019 --> 00:31:18,839
[SPEAKER_00] takvu molitvu.

602
00:31:18,839 --> 00:31:20,920
[SPEAKER_00] Postoji dublja molitva.

603
00:31:20,920 --> 00:31:22,940
[SPEAKER_00] Dakle, ja govorim,

604
00:31:22,940 --> 00:31:23,539
[SPEAKER_00] Bog čuje.

605
00:31:23,539 --> 00:31:25,339
[SPEAKER_00] Dakle, to je molitva

606
00:31:25,339 --> 00:31:26,000
[SPEAKER_00] koja se rađa

607
00:31:26,000 --> 00:31:26,859
[SPEAKER_00] iz moje nutrine

608
00:31:26,859 --> 00:31:28,599
[SPEAKER_00] i moje svijesti

609
00:31:28,599 --> 00:31:29,660
[SPEAKER_00] da mi je Bog potreban,

610
00:31:29,660 --> 00:31:30,660
[SPEAKER_00] da bez Boga ne mogu.

611
00:31:30,660 --> 00:31:32,960
[SPEAKER_00] Ona se rađa iz srca.

612
00:31:32,960 --> 00:31:33,940
[SPEAKER_00] Ja volim reći ljudima

613
00:31:33,940 --> 00:31:34,539
[SPEAKER_00] kad me govore,

614
00:31:34,539 --> 00:31:36,500
[SPEAKER_00] kad traži savjet o molitvi,

615
00:31:36,500 --> 00:31:38,000
[SPEAKER_00] ako te molitva ne mijenja,

616
00:31:38,000 --> 00:31:38,740
[SPEAKER_00] mijenjaj molitvu.

617
00:31:38,740 --> 00:31:40,619
[SPEAKER_00] Molitva te mora mijenjati.

618
00:31:40,619 --> 00:31:42,359
[SPEAKER_00] Moraš postati bolja osoba,

619
00:31:42,359 --> 00:31:43,819
[SPEAKER_00] plemenitija,

620
00:31:44,559 --> 00:31:45,700
[SPEAKER_00] spremljenija opraštati,

621
00:31:45,700 --> 00:31:46,900
[SPEAKER_00] spremljenija činiti dobro.

622
00:31:46,900 --> 00:31:47,960
[SPEAKER_00] Ako se to ne događa

623
00:31:47,960 --> 00:31:48,259
[SPEAKER_00] s molitva,

624
00:31:48,259 --> 00:31:48,980
[SPEAKER_00] nešto nije u redu.

625
00:31:48,980 --> 00:31:51,180
[SPEAKER_00] Na ovom razini ja govorim,

626
00:31:51,180 --> 00:31:51,880
[SPEAKER_00] Bog me čuje,

627
00:31:51,880 --> 00:31:53,980
[SPEAKER_00] molitva se rađa iz srca.

628
00:31:53,980 --> 00:31:55,720
[SPEAKER_00] Jer se rađa iz srca,

629
00:31:55,720 --> 00:31:56,880
[SPEAKER_00] ulazi u Božje srce

630
00:31:56,880 --> 00:31:57,779
[SPEAKER_00] i Bog je čuje.

631
00:31:57,779 --> 00:32:00,000
[SPEAKER_00] I ta molitva postaje kanal,

632
00:32:00,000 --> 00:32:02,119
[SPEAKER_00] postaje kanal po kojem sadržaj

633
00:32:02,119 --> 00:32:03,400
[SPEAKER_00] iz Božje srca se pretaču

634
00:32:03,400 --> 00:32:04,160
[SPEAKER_00] u moje srce.

635
00:32:04,160 --> 00:32:06,140
[SPEAKER_00] Ali postoji još dublja molitva.

636
00:32:06,140 --> 00:32:08,240
[SPEAKER_00] Bog govori, ja čujem.

637
00:32:08,240 --> 00:32:10,000
[SPEAKER_00] Mi smo zaboravili šutjeti.

638
00:32:10,000 --> 00:32:11,299
[SPEAKER_00] Nas previše riječi,

639
00:32:14,559 --> 00:32:16,160
[SPEAKER_00] banjska tišina,

640
00:32:16,160 --> 00:32:17,099
[SPEAKER_00] nutrenja sabranost

641
00:32:17,099 --> 00:32:18,920
[SPEAKER_00] su dva važna preduvjeta

642
00:32:18,920 --> 00:32:19,579
[SPEAKER_00] za molitvu.

643
00:32:19,579 --> 00:32:21,380
[SPEAKER_00] Molitva je u biti,

644
00:32:21,380 --> 00:32:22,900
[SPEAKER_00] ispravna molitva ima

645
00:32:22,900 --> 00:32:25,900
[SPEAKER_00] dva nužna uvjeta,

646
00:32:25,900 --> 00:32:27,640
[SPEAKER_00] a to je pozornost

647
00:32:27,640 --> 00:32:28,660
[SPEAKER_00] i pobožnost.

648
00:32:28,660 --> 00:32:30,940
[SPEAKER_00] Ako nema toga,

649
00:32:30,940 --> 00:32:32,339
[SPEAKER_00] pobožnost je ništa drugo

650
00:32:32,339 --> 00:32:32,920
[SPEAKER_00] nego ljubav prema

651
00:32:32,920 --> 00:32:33,700
[SPEAKER_00] gospodinu Bogu.

652
00:32:33,700 --> 00:32:35,380
[SPEAKER_00] Ako nema ove sabranosti,

653
00:32:35,380 --> 00:32:37,880
[SPEAKER_00] ako nema ovog napora

654
00:32:37,880 --> 00:32:39,640
[SPEAKER_00] da ja uđem u dijalog,

655
00:32:39,640 --> 00:32:41,359
[SPEAKER_00] u razgovor s gospodinom Bogom,

656
00:32:41,680 --> 00:32:42,240
[SPEAKER_00] nema molitve,

657
00:32:42,240 --> 00:32:43,420
[SPEAKER_00] postaje samo na klapanje.

658
00:32:43,420 --> 00:32:44,779
[SPEAKER_00] Dakle,

659
00:32:44,779 --> 00:32:47,400
[SPEAKER_00] kad dođem do stupnja

660
00:32:47,400 --> 00:32:48,940
[SPEAKER_00] da mi je tišina važna,

661
00:32:48,940 --> 00:32:50,339
[SPEAKER_00] da se povlačem u sebe,

662
00:32:50,339 --> 00:32:52,920
[SPEAKER_00] tada ću ja uspijeti čuti

663
00:32:52,920 --> 00:32:54,640
[SPEAKER_00] što Bog govori crkvi.

664
00:32:54,640 --> 00:32:55,500
[SPEAKER_00] Odnosno u mom srcu.

665
00:32:55,500 --> 00:32:57,519
[SPEAKER_00] Matamo negdje u knjize utkrivenja,

666
00:32:57,519 --> 00:32:59,200
[SPEAKER_00] duh govori crkvama,

667
00:32:59,200 --> 00:33:00,819
[SPEAKER_00] duh govori crkvu,

668
00:33:00,819 --> 00:33:01,519
[SPEAKER_00] Efezu si miri.

669
00:33:01,519 --> 00:33:02,940
[SPEAKER_00] Duh govori meni,

670
00:33:02,940 --> 00:33:03,539
[SPEAKER_00] mojoj crkvi,

671
00:33:03,539 --> 00:33:04,180
[SPEAKER_00] mom srcu.

672
00:33:04,180 --> 00:33:05,700
[SPEAKER_00] Ali trebam doći do toga

673
00:33:05,700 --> 00:33:07,480
[SPEAKER_00] da ja čujem što duh poručuje.

674
00:33:07,480 --> 00:33:09,420
[SPEAKER_00] Jer duh u meni progovara.

675
00:33:10,019 --> 00:33:12,740
[SPEAKER_00] duh mi otkriva volju očevu

676
00:33:12,740 --> 00:33:14,259
[SPEAKER_00] i daj bi snagu da je izvršim.

677
00:33:14,259 --> 00:33:16,259
[SPEAKER_00] Ali moram se nauči šutjeti.

678
00:33:16,259 --> 00:33:18,960
[SPEAKER_00] Moram nauči se povlačiti u svoju,

679
00:33:18,960 --> 00:33:19,420
[SPEAKER_00] kaže Isus,

680
00:33:19,420 --> 00:33:20,859
[SPEAKER_00] povući se u svoju sobu.

681
00:33:20,859 --> 00:33:22,640
[SPEAKER_00] To može bih fizička soba,

682
00:33:22,640 --> 00:33:23,980
[SPEAKER_00] ali češće je soba svog srca.

683
00:33:23,980 --> 00:33:25,440
[SPEAKER_00] Povući se u svoju nutrinu,

684
00:33:25,440 --> 00:33:28,099
[SPEAKER_00] tu osluškuj što duh poručuje crkvi.

685
00:33:28,099 --> 00:33:29,440
[SPEAKER_00] Što duh poručuje ti.

686
00:33:29,700 --> 00:33:31,079
[SPEAKER_00] Treba puno rada na sebi,

687
00:33:31,079 --> 00:33:32,819
[SPEAKER_00] puno,

688
00:33:32,819 --> 00:33:35,519
[SPEAKER_00] puno, puno truda

689
00:33:35,519 --> 00:33:37,460
[SPEAKER_00] da se osvoji ta sabranu,

690
00:33:37,460 --> 00:33:38,299
[SPEAKER_00] da se sačuva

691
00:33:38,299 --> 00:33:39,759
[SPEAKER_00] i da omogućim duhu

692
00:33:39,759 --> 00:33:41,059
[SPEAKER_00] da progovori mom srcu.

693
00:33:41,059 --> 00:33:42,420
[SPEAKER_00] Na još dobljoj razini,

694
00:33:42,420 --> 00:33:43,240
[SPEAKER_00] četvrtoj razini,

695
00:33:43,240 --> 00:33:44,700
[SPEAKER_00] Bog govori

696
00:33:44,700 --> 00:33:46,180
[SPEAKER_00] i Bog sluša.

697
00:33:46,180 --> 00:33:48,019
[SPEAKER_00] To je već mistična molitva.

698
00:33:48,019 --> 00:33:49,880
[SPEAKER_00] Kad osoba doživljava

699
00:33:49,880 --> 00:33:50,759
[SPEAKER_00] da se udijeluje u životu

700
00:33:50,759 --> 00:33:51,700
[SPEAKER_00] predstavu trojstva,

701
00:33:52,099 --> 00:33:54,039
[SPEAKER_00] da je otac izgovara u sinu,

702
00:33:54,039 --> 00:33:55,380
[SPEAKER_00] ti si moj dijete ljubljeno,

703
00:33:55,380 --> 00:33:56,660
[SPEAKER_00] a ja, moj duh,

704
00:33:56,660 --> 00:33:58,460
[SPEAKER_00] sa Isom Kristom u duhu svetom

705
00:33:58,460 --> 00:33:58,819
[SPEAKER_00] dogovara,

706
00:33:58,819 --> 00:33:59,799
[SPEAKER_00] Abba, oče,

707
00:33:59,799 --> 00:34:01,099
[SPEAKER_00] nek se vrši tvoja volja.

708
00:34:01,099 --> 00:34:03,119
[SPEAKER_00] To je mistična molitva

709
00:34:03,119 --> 00:34:05,099
[SPEAKER_00] da od dragi Boga

710
00:34:05,099 --> 00:34:06,019
[SPEAKER_00] bi svi došli do toga,

711
00:34:06,019 --> 00:34:07,180
[SPEAKER_00] ali redovito mali broj

712
00:34:07,180 --> 00:34:08,019
[SPEAKER_00] do toga dolazi.

713
00:34:08,019 --> 00:34:08,519
[SPEAKER_00] E sada,

714
00:34:08,519 --> 00:34:10,219
[SPEAKER_00] konkretno to znači ovo.

715
00:34:10,219 --> 00:34:13,000
[SPEAKER_00] Treba u početku duhovnog života

716
00:34:13,000 --> 00:34:15,139
[SPEAKER_00] usvojiti jednu molitvenu metodu.

717
00:34:15,139 --> 00:34:16,519
[SPEAKER_00] Najko je reći,

718
00:34:16,519 --> 00:34:17,639
[SPEAKER_00] pa molit ću se,

719
00:34:17,639 --> 00:34:18,880
[SPEAKER_00] kaj idem spavat,

720
00:34:18,880 --> 00:34:19,880
[SPEAKER_00] učinit ću znak križa

721
00:34:19,880 --> 00:34:21,119
[SPEAKER_00] i anđelu Čuvaru.

722
00:34:21,119 --> 00:34:23,139
[SPEAKER_00] To je kao kad bi ja rekao

723
00:34:23,139 --> 00:34:23,860
[SPEAKER_00] čega živiš,

724
00:34:23,860 --> 00:34:25,440
[SPEAKER_00] kaže, uzmam tri zličice mlijeka

725
00:34:25,440 --> 00:34:26,019
[SPEAKER_00] svaki dan.

726
00:34:26,019 --> 00:34:27,820
[SPEAKER_00] Pa neće baš dugo živjeti.

727
00:34:27,820 --> 00:34:29,840
[SPEAKER_00] Treba se dobro hraniti.

728
00:34:29,840 --> 00:34:31,099
[SPEAKER_00] I naš duh je potreban

729
00:34:31,099 --> 00:34:31,860
[SPEAKER_00] dobre hrane.

730
00:34:31,860 --> 00:34:34,599
[SPEAKER_00] Molitva je hrana duše,

731
00:34:34,599 --> 00:34:36,599
[SPEAKER_00] a to znači da je jako važno

732
00:34:36,599 --> 00:34:37,480
[SPEAKER_00] u početku duhovnog života

733
00:34:37,480 --> 00:34:39,079
[SPEAKER_00] osvojiti jednu molitvenu metodu.

734
00:34:39,079 --> 00:34:40,599
[SPEAKER_00] Postoji razne molitvene metode.

735
00:34:40,599 --> 00:34:43,280
[SPEAKER_00] Ja redovito studentima teologije

736
00:34:43,280 --> 00:34:45,179
[SPEAKER_00] sogerira nešto što je crkva

737
00:34:45,179 --> 00:34:46,760
[SPEAKER_00] iznijedila stoljećima,

738
00:34:46,760 --> 00:34:48,260
[SPEAKER_00] stoljećima duhovnog rasta

739
00:34:48,260 --> 00:34:49,880
[SPEAKER_00] unutar monaške duhovnosti,

740
00:34:49,880 --> 00:34:51,119
[SPEAKER_00] a ta se metoda zove

741
00:34:51,119 --> 00:34:52,599
[SPEAKER_00] lekcijo divina.

742
00:34:52,599 --> 00:34:54,659
[SPEAKER_00] A to znači molitveni sustreć

743
00:34:54,659 --> 00:34:55,679
[SPEAKER_00] sa riječom Božijom.

744
00:34:55,679 --> 00:34:57,019
[SPEAKER_00] Da svaki dan

745
00:34:57,019 --> 00:34:58,699
[SPEAKER_00] otvaran svetopismo,

746
00:34:58,699 --> 00:35:00,719
[SPEAKER_00] najbolje možda evanđelje od dana,

747
00:35:00,719 --> 00:35:03,079
[SPEAKER_00] da na tom Božijom riječu

748
00:35:03,079 --> 00:35:04,099
[SPEAKER_00] koja je živa,

749
00:35:04,099 --> 00:35:05,219
[SPEAKER_00] koja je djelotvorna,

750
00:35:05,219 --> 00:35:05,400
[SPEAKER_00] kaže,

751
00:35:05,400 --> 00:35:06,260
[SPEAKER_00] potrebno se hebrajima,

752
00:35:06,260 --> 00:35:07,920
[SPEAKER_00] oštrija od vosijekog mača,

753
00:35:07,920 --> 00:35:09,340
[SPEAKER_00] sila za unašnu utrinu,

754
00:35:09,340 --> 00:35:10,719
[SPEAKER_00] ona me rasvjetljava,

755
00:35:10,719 --> 00:35:12,760
[SPEAKER_00] ona mi otkriva mene meni,

756
00:35:12,760 --> 00:35:14,579
[SPEAKER_00] otkriva mi Božji pogled na mene,

757
00:35:15,019 --> 00:35:16,940
[SPEAKER_00] i onda tom riječu osvjetljena,

758
00:35:16,940 --> 00:35:18,699
[SPEAKER_00] ona mi postaje program moga života,

759
00:35:18,699 --> 00:35:20,280
[SPEAKER_00] postaje hrana moga življenja.

760
00:35:20,280 --> 00:35:22,480
[SPEAKER_00] To je možda najbolja metoda,

761
00:35:22,480 --> 00:35:24,960
[SPEAKER_00] svakako za vjeru učitelje,

762
00:35:24,960 --> 00:35:26,179
[SPEAKER_00] za studenti teologije,

763
00:35:26,179 --> 00:35:27,619
[SPEAKER_00] za intelektualce,

764
00:35:27,619 --> 00:35:31,239
[SPEAKER_00] možda za ljude koji nemaju,

765
00:35:31,239 --> 00:35:31,619
[SPEAKER_00] možda,

766
00:35:31,619 --> 00:35:33,460
[SPEAKER_00] sklonost čitanju,

767
00:35:33,460 --> 00:35:34,900
[SPEAKER_00] ili ovoj vrstni molitve,

768
00:35:34,900 --> 00:35:37,119
[SPEAKER_00] molitva krunice je jako dobra,

769
00:35:37,219 --> 00:35:39,980
[SPEAKER_00] ali mora bi povezana sa razmatranjem.

770
00:35:39,980 --> 00:35:41,239
[SPEAKER_00] Moram se,

771
00:35:41,239 --> 00:35:42,199
[SPEAKER_00] evo,

772
00:35:42,199 --> 00:35:44,679
[SPEAKER_00] naučiti,

773
00:35:44,679 --> 00:35:46,599
[SPEAKER_00] moram učiniti dodatan napor,

774
00:35:46,599 --> 00:35:49,019
[SPEAKER_00] da svoj duh usmjeri prema otajstvima

775
00:35:49,019 --> 00:35:50,280
[SPEAKER_00] gospodina Isusa Krista,

776
00:35:50,280 --> 00:35:51,079
[SPEAKER_00] njegova života,

777
00:35:51,079 --> 00:35:53,320
[SPEAKER_00] i onda u Marijinoj školi

778
00:35:53,320 --> 00:35:55,280
[SPEAKER_00] ja otkrivam ljepotu

779
00:35:55,280 --> 00:35:56,639
[SPEAKER_00] i dubine Kristova otajstva,

780
00:35:56,639 --> 00:35:57,739
[SPEAKER_00] ljepotu Kristova lica,

781
00:35:57,739 --> 00:36:00,539
[SPEAKER_00] i tako u meni onda raste duhovni život.

782
00:36:01,239 --> 00:36:01,980
[SPEAKER_01] Dragi domladene,

783
00:36:01,980 --> 00:36:03,920
[SPEAKER_01] hvala vam što ste gostovali danas,

784
00:36:03,920 --> 00:36:05,000
[SPEAKER_01] što ste bili s nama.

785
00:36:05,000 --> 00:36:06,820
[SPEAKER_01] Neka nam ovo svima bude poticaj

786
00:36:06,820 --> 00:36:08,380
[SPEAKER_01] za bogatiji duhovni život.

787
00:36:08,380 --> 00:36:10,000
[SPEAKER_01] Vama, dragi gledatelji,

788
00:36:10,000 --> 00:36:11,280
[SPEAKER_01] hvala puno na gledanju.

789
00:36:11,280 --> 00:36:13,239
[SPEAKER_01] Pozivamo vas da budete s nama

790
00:36:13,239 --> 00:36:14,440
[SPEAKER_01] i u idućinem misijama.

791
00:36:14,440 --> 00:36:15,260
[SPEAKER_01] Pratite nas.

792
00:36:15,260 --> 00:36:16,340
[SPEAKER_01] Boži blagoslov.

793
00:36:19,920 --> 00:36:32,699
[UNKNOWN] Hvala vam što ste.

